    caption: [*Nereis virens* (A–D) and *Nereis diversicolor* (E) are errant polychaetes. A, Anterior end, with pharynx everted. B, External structure. C, Posterior end. D, Generalized transverse section through region of the intestine. E, In this photo of a live *N. diversicolor*, note the well-defined segments, the lobed parapodia, and the prostomium with tentacles.],
    path: "../fig/fig-2025-11-20-11-47-32.png"
